Ranger Help for: furyfire
=========================

SYNTAX:      furyfire <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     80
SKILL TYPE:  archery

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to unleash a rapid volley of arrows from a
shortbow, firing 3 to 4 arrows in quick succession at the target. The
Ranger must have a shortbow wielded and at least 4 arrows in inventory.
Each arrow is rolled individually for hit and damage. Furyfire is one
of the most devastating ranged attacks available, but its high SP cost
and ammunition requirements make it best saved for tough opponents.
